* Core Constraints

-------
Namecapce: fr.liglab.adele.cube.core
-------

*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| <<Predicate Name>> | <<Arity>>        | <<checking>>  | <<finding>> | <<performing>> | <<Small Description>> |
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./find-locally.html}find-locally}}   | Unary             | no          | yes        | no           | When specified for a given variable, it will help to find a value for it while resolving this constrained variable.  |
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./on-node.html}on-node}}	|  Binary	|  yes	|  yes	|  yes	|  Garanties that a Component is on a particular Node | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./in-scope.html}in-scope}}	|  Binary	|  yes	|  yes	|  yes	|  Garanties that a Node is on a particular Scope |  
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./connect.html}connect}}	|  Binary	|  yes	|  yes	|  yes	|  Garanties that a Component is Connected to another Component | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./in-components.html}in-components}}	|  Unary | 	 yes	|  no	|  no	|  Ensure that a component has at max the defined number of Input Components | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./out-components.html}out-components}}	|  Unary	|  yes	|  no	|  no	|  Ensure that a component has at max the defined number of Output Components | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./self-create-locally.html}self-create-locally}}	|  Unary	|  no	|  yes	|  no	|  Create a new instance locally of the same type as the provided variable | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./components-per-node.html}components-per-node}}	|  Unary	|  yes	|  no	|  no	|  Ensure that will be a max number of component instances on the given node | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./components-per-scope.html}components-per-scope}}	|  Unary	|  yes	|  yes	|  no	|  Ensure that will be a max number of component instances on the given scope | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
| {{{./self-sizing.html}self-sizing}}	|  Binary	|  yes	|  yes	|  yes	|  increase the number of particular components per node when its in-components are saturated | 
*----------------:--------------:-----------:---------:------------:-------------------:
